      "rationale": "Model setup reviewed by a second FDA analyst using a 47-item modeling checklist. No setup errors identified. Boundary conditions, contact definitions, and material assignments independently verified. Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/factor/model-form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
