      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model inputs (geometry, material, boundary conditions) demonstrably equivalent to experimental test conditions for each of the 11 constructs.",
      "rationale": "Specimen-specific FEA models built using CMM-measured geometry for each of the 11 constructs. Material properties assigned from lot-specific coupon data. Boundary conditions replicate the ASTM F1717 test fixture kinematics as confirmed by fixture compliance measurements. Equivalency demonstrated for all three QoIs. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/factor/output-comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
