      "rationale": "Validation metric E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 9 for stiffness (0.87), yield force (1.12), and force at 40 mm (1.44). All below the 1.96 threshold. Percent differences 4.2%, 6.1%, and 7.8% respectively, all below 10%. Gradation 3 achieved for all three QoIs."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/factor/relevance-qoi",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
