      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in the FDA guidance on spinal implant testing and are directly predictive of fatigue life and clinical failure risk. The same QoIs appear in the 510(k) submission comparison table. Gradation 3 achieved."
